<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986479>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Atopida, morphological details. A) A. castanea, head, anterior view; B) same, ventral portion of prosternum and mesoventrite; C) A. insularis sp. nov., ventral portion of head, prosternum and mesoventrite; D) same, head and pronotum, dorsal view; E) A. lescheni sp. nov., male, head, projection of supraantennal ridge marked with arrow; F) A. suturalis, female, head, projection of supraantennal ridge marked with arrow. Abbreviations: mp—mesoventral process, pp—prosternal process, sgr—subgenal ridge, soc—subocular carina." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986479/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986483>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Atopida suturalis, mouthparts. A) mandible, B) maxilla, C) labrum, D) labium. Scale bar = 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986483/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986489>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Atopida, pronotum. A) A. castanea, male; B) same, female; C) A. hirta, male; D) same, female; E) A. impressa, male; F) same, female; G) A. insularis sp. nov., male; H) same, female; I) A. lescheni sp. nov., male; J) A. montana, male; K) same, female; L) A. paparoa sp. nov., male; M) same, female; N) A. paringa sp. nov., male; O) A. proba, male; P) same, female; Q) A. suffusa, male; R) same, female; S) A. suturalis, male; T) same, female; U) A. tuhua sp. nov., male; V) same, female; W) A. villosa, male; X) same, female; Y) A. waipoua sp. nov., male; Z) A. walkerae sp. nov., male; AA) A. westlandensis sp. nov., male; BB) same, female. Not to the same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986489/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986491>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Atopida, hind wings. A) A. suturalis, macropterous wing; B) A. impressa brachypterous wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986491/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986493>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Atopida, male terminal segments and genitalia (A, C) and gut contents (B). A) A. suturalis, B) same, gut contents, C) A. paparoa sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986493/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986501>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Atopida, abdominal segments of females. A) A. castanea; B) A. hirta; C) A. impressa; D) same, tergite VII; E) A. insularis sp. nov.; F) A. montana, male; G) A. paparoa sp. nov.; H) A. proba; I) same, tergite VII; J) A. suffusa; K) A. suturalis; L) same, tergite VII; M) A. tuhua; N) A. villosa; O) A. westlandensis sp. nov. Not to the same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986501/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6986505>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Atopida, female genital tract. A) A. insularis sp. nov., B) A. villosa. Abbreviations: bscl—bursal sclerite, gla— gland, sVIII—sternite VIII, tVIII—tergite VIII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6986505/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

